lead_paragraph: Canada's Davis Cup hopes received a double blow on Monday when world number 13 Milos Raonic and top doubles player Daniel Nestor pulled out of next weekend's first-round tie against France in Guadeloupe.

headline.print_headline: Canada's Davis Cup Hopes Hit as Raonic and Nestor Pull Out
